<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause xmlns:xt="urn:xpressauthor:trackchanges" id="_866b1a83-1f4e-416b-85f6-c005745e16bf" outputclass="ncc-clause"><meta><facet building="Class 2"/><facet building="Class 3"/><facet building="Class 4"/><facet building="Class 5"/><facet building="Class 6"/><facet building="Class 7a"/><facet building="Class 7b"/><facet building="Class 8"/><facet building="Class 9a"/><facet building="Class 9b"/><facet building="Class 9c"/></meta><sptc>H1O1</sptc><title id="_0ba228ea-2cae-475b-a759-2577446d37fe">Objective</title><archive-num>2019: O2.1</archive-num><subclause id="_dadb3f2c-e4d2-418a-abc1-e4d42086d865" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_a1e99c13-0d42-4059-8f98-96850697d0b7">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>The Objective is to—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_b86aa18e-c5f9-4410-9131-e9bc6fff4c7f">safeguard people from injury caused by structural failure; and</li><li id="_04c45169-4f5b-43ce-97e0-009ff41fe779">safeguard people from loss of <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1186_0.6.0.xml#_905252bf-2ff1-43f8-ae81-2949aa116fee" id="_db69de91-ed7f-4258-aa7f-3e65ffaeac88" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">amenity</xref> caused by structural behaviour; and</li><li id="_18f40850-426d-46a9-8019-69ea8d9acd78">protect <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1387_0.4.0.xml#_ffbca87e-eb18-4463-a6fb-e59b79881fa3" id="_9166b1d2-8860-4dbf-9b3d-dda5bf4b71f1" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">other property</xref> from physical damage caused by structural failure; and</li><li id="_e200b5fa-26af-4f65-b105-16647af4ee9e">safeguard people from injury that may be caused by failure of, or impact with, glazing.</li></ol></subclause></clause>